  <p>Sets the basic color of the pipeline, used when no lighting is enabled.</p>  <p>Note that if you don't add any layers to the pipeline then the color
will be blended unmodified with the destination; the default blend
expects premultiplied colors: for example, use (0.5, 0.0, 0.0, 0.5) for
semi-transparent red. See <link xref="Cogl.Color.premultiply"/>.</p>  <p>The default value is (1.0, 1.0, 1.0, 1.0)</p>
  <p>Since 2.0</p>
